descriptionHtml:
Wild Animal Photo Editor – Photo Frames, Sticker app is specially designed for Wild Animal lovers. It can be used to show love towards wild animal and spread the message like Save Animal, Save Lion, Save Tiger, Save Elephant, Save Rhinoceros, Save Camel, Save Panda, Save Horse, Save Kangaroo, Save Black Bear, Save Deer, Save Giraffe, Save Monkey, Save Zebra.

Make selfie photo with dangerous wild species of animals with the help you of this photo Editor. 4K and Ultra HD quality photo backgrounds and animal stickers will give super natural effect to your images and selfies. Your final photo with these photo “background images”, effects, stickers and text message will differentiate you among others.

Feel yourself surrounded with natural beauty of wild and beautiful animals and show your thrilling, unforgettable and exciting moments with Wild Animals. Unique “photo editor”, “foto frame”. Creative Animal “photo frame”. HD “photo editor app”.

Best “Background Eraser” app. Change your photo with natural looking background and wild animal photo sticker and give a daring and dashing look to your photography. Wild animal photo editor contains lot of natural backgrounds and animal photos stickers. This app also known as, picture editor, picture frame, animal photo frames, animal DP maker, photo editor, foto frame, poto editor, foto editor, photo background editor, photo maker, image editor, background changer, auto cut paste photo, auto cut out photo editor, cut paste photo editor.

Wild Animal “Poto Editor” Photo Frames, Sticker is beautiful app that contains following animals sticker :-

👍 Lion Photos
👍Rhinoceros Photos
👍Tiger Photos
👍Camel Photos
👍Zebra Photos
👍Elephant Photos
👍Bear Photos
👍Kangaroo Photos
👍Deer Photos
👍Panda Photos
👍Giraffe Photos
👍Monkey Photos
👍Horse Photos

Amazing Tools & Features:
◆ Photo crop
◆ Auto Erase Magic tool to erase photos background automatically
◆ Manual Erase tool
◆ Undo, Redo & Restore tool
◆ Zoom in and Zoom out feature
◆ Add Beautiful Stickers
◆ Write Text Message
◆ Change Background Theme
◆ Apply Beautiful Photo Effects
◆ Change For Ground and Background Image on easy tap

How to use this App?
1. Choose any image from gallery or take selfie.
2. Crop the image as required.
3. Erase tool: Touch the unwanted part of the photo to erase. Use Auto Erase tool to Auto Erase Photo
4. Use Restore tool to set photo offset and radius.
5. Use Zoom tool to zoom in and zoom out image.
6. Use Bg button to select backgrounds or change default background
7. Use Effect button to give various effects on photo.
8. Tap on Flip button to flip the photo.
9. Tap on Sticker button to add animal stickers.
10.Add Text message by clicking on text button.
11.Click on sticker to button to add emoji.
12. Save your Final Creations using Save Button.
13. Share Image via Social media like Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Instagram etc.
descriptionShort: Easily Create DP, Profile, Wallpaper or status Photo as you want this app.
